comment:
* Structure designed to hold the data related to a specific request across the various
     * callbacks needed to complete it.

variables.name: nativeResultObject
variables.comment: Native object to post the result to.

variables.name: accountManager
variables.comment: Reference to the account manager to use for the various requests.

variables.name: options
variables.comment: Authenticator-specific options for the request, used for AccountManager#getAuthToken.

variables.name: authTokenType
variables.comment: Desired token type, used for AccountManager#getAuthToken.

variables.name: account
variables.comment: Account to fetch an auth token for.
